videos.description: Jordan Wright battles for an offensive rebound and Vanderbilt swings the ball around the perimeter until Maxwell Evans knocks down the wide-open 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Great ball movement sets up Vandy's 3) 2020/02/11

videos.headline: Great ball movement sets up Vandy's 3

videos.description: Kentucky's Ashton Hagan can't convert at the rim, but Nick Richards is there to clean up with the putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Richards flushes putback slam for Kentucky) 2020/02/11

videos.headline: Richards flushes putback slam for Kentucky

videos.description: NBA legend Scottie Pippen is in attendance at Vanderbilt Memorial Gymnasium to watch his son, Scotty Pippen Jr., take on Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Scottie Pippen on hand to watch son play Kentucky) 2020/02/11

videos.headline: Scottie Pippen on hand to watch son play Kentucky

videos.description: Vanderbilt's Dylan Disu rises up for a dunk over Nick Richards, but Richards swats the shot away with authority.
videos.headline: Richards denies poster attempt

videos.description: Ashton Hagan grabs a defensive rebound and passes ahead to Tyrese Maxey, who throws down a double-clutch dunk on the fast break for Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maxey leaks out for transition jam) 2020/02/11

videos.headline: Maxey leaks out for transition jam

videos.description: Tyrese Maxey hoists up a shot from deep and the ball bounces high above the backboard and down through the net for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maxey gets friendly roll on Kentucky's 3-ball) 2020/02/11

videos.headline: Maxey gets friendly roll on Kentucky's 3-ball

videos.description: Kentucky's Ashton Hagans dishes a one-handed pass between two defenders and finds Nick Richards under the hoop for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hagans threads the needle to Richards for the slam) 2020/02/11

videos.headline: Hagans threads the needle to Richards for the slam
